		<poi type="ul.ulsl.sm.tut" mapid="15" xpos="-461.7855" ypos="21.47931" zpos="377.3728" guid="fGm5nebxaEmT/Jr1PMJZaA==" cull="CounterClockwise" rotate="100,0,100" info="[- TIER ONE XP BUFFS -] &#xA;&#xA;These are all considered tier 1 because they are cheap & super easy to get. &#xA;&#xA;• [Experience Booster] - Super easy to get and only cost 1 laurel if you don't have any sitting around. &#xA;&#xA;• [Guild XP Gain] - Visit a maxed guild hall and talk to the bartender.&#xA;(If you are using the [Candy Corn Gobbler] for this buff, use it in WvW and you will have higher chances)&#xA;&#xA;• [New Year's Gift] - Only 5% but they are super cheap. If you use them mounted you wont get transformed and you can use 24 at a time to stack up to 2 hours worth of the buff." inforange="6" miniMapVisibility="0" mapvisibility="0" iconsize="3" heightOffset="3" iconfile="data/sl/TutTemplateT1.png" />
		<poi type="ul.ulsl.sm.tut" mapid="15" xpos="-461.5201" ypos="21.22214" zpos="367.4626" guid="8tusgnKAvUSCUPw9cuTgLA==" cull="CounterClockwise" rotate="100,0,70" info="[- TIER TWO XP BUFFS -]&#xA;&#xA;These are all considered tier 2 because they are a bit harder to get or require masteries or events.&#xA;&#xA;• [Festival Gobbler Boost] - Must be purchased with gems during the festivals.&#xA;&#xA;• [Celebration Bonus] - Limited ways to attain these. Weekly Wizards Vault and a few other methods and thats it.&#xA;&#xA;• [Rested] - If you log out in Arborstone while sitting in a char AND have Arborstone Revitalization maxed this is an amazing buff. It does take prep and masteries to get.&#xA;&#xA;• [Guild Banner] - If you dont do a lot of guild missions or know how to get these, they can be a bit of a pain to get and only last 30 min." inforange="6" miniMapVisibility="0" mapvisibility="0" iconsize="3" heightOffset="3" iconfile="data/sl/TutTemplateT2.png" />
